<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Norman_Vincent_Peale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
